itunes:title: KYLE RITTENHOUSE LIVE
title: KYLE RITTENHOUSE LIVE
description:
From the main stage of AmericaFest, in his first public appearance since his acquittal, Kyle Rittenhouse is joined by an all star panel comprised of Human Events Daily Host Jack Posobiec, Elijah Schaffer, Drew Hernandez and founder of Turning Point USA Charlie Kirk! Revisit the epic discussion that chronicles Kyle’s journey from the ashes and lies of Kenosha to the joy of truth, liberty and justice.

Here is your daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
